detaileddescription.para: Used for identification of the language. The identification should not be translated. It should be replaced by the name of the language in Persian using lower-case characters only (e.g. "czech", "japanese", "russian", etc.). It should be equal to the identification used in language.cpp.
The Persian LaTeX does not use such commands. Because of this the empty string is returned in this implementation.
